Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出航准备进行得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 即将完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰10分钟后 从卫星明斯利启航
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军登上了卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要以叛逃者的名义逮捕舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军在抓舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以必须赶快离开这颗卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧准备出航 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.13,0:03:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米莉和迪克也去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特要去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生要我穿好机师服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和联邦军作对…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还多说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE确实可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是… 没想到会和联邦军为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕的话 现在下船也不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃尔夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉甘 分清轻重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛时 偶尔也会遇上不利的车道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不能丢掉必胜的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即将从卫星内航行 转换为外宇宙航行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统探测到舰船反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到识别信号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军所属 达维恩级宇宙战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅雷 日晕 看守者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.21,0:04:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会以为那样就结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克·艾诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想轻易逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些叛逃者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来逮捕我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会被怎么处置？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要逮捕我们最好的办法是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在舰船开动前实施控制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 歌姬号就无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这么做就说明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放马出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个也别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包围他们 舰船就是他们的监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真老老实实出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自信满满吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克不只是个优秀的电脑工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说还有过人的参谋企划能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才被提拔为阿雷克斯基地的副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得舰长也吃了他的亏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 那种宪兵队的差事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不符合我的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关键是 没想到高达会来搅局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为军舰上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这种情形更让人兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴奋是可以 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心吃多上火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的大脑满负荷运转时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 让我看看你的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克·艾诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通知机动战士部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体机动战士准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}重复 全体机动战士…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要打了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可都是联邦军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要出动机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么阴谋吗 古鲁迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要跟着他们的节奏走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随时待命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 焰火伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 信号弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么光？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光弹障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战术虽然略显古典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作用却一目了然不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼叫歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:07:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线路接通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是地球联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八宇宙舰队特别分遣舰队司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特拉·葛瓦班中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们已经被完全包围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即解除武装 乖乖投降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则 就认定你们为敌对势力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发动总攻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.26,0:08:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用枪指着人家 还装正人君子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是担任歌姬号航行总管的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当斯·提尼尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不打算与联邦军为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克舰长在个人调查中发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE躲藏在被弃置的宇宙要塞安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚当斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们认为 现在正是对UE发起反击的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次作战一旦成功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必能对UE造成重大打击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 葛瓦班中校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望第八宇宙舰队网开一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 你提供的情报很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那是上级部门应该考虑的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军人不可以擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果还是个军人就该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是逮捕古鲁迪克·艾诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 给个答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不作答吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:40.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迫不得已 我们只能强制执行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先安排高达躲入卫星的阴影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开索敌系统侦测
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的损失怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光束枪被击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三台杰诺亚斯安然无恙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装腔作势
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 多半不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被舰队的火控系统锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有部署在周围的机动战士部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候出动的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光弹的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪光弹发射后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.09,0:11:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用数台机动战士牵制歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸引我们注意力的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出动了其他部队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在被他们耍着玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 看你怎么办 古鲁迪克
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会老老实实投降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实就算他们顽抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且击沉我们一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩余的两艘必会击沉歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归根结底死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我们已经扳回了劣势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们…还藏有舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.25,0:12:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炮击不久将歇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么停止攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会 因为同是联邦军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心生怜悯了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还须前往攻略安巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要尽可能避免消耗弹药和舰只
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:13:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古鲁迪克的想法无非是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为另有目的 所以不想做无谓的牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集结了这么多战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他难道真打算去讨伐UE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们必须履行职责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 还有什么招数？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击来自舰队后方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情况不明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙难道还有增援？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统没有捕捉到任何目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这反应是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UE！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索敌系统捕捉到目标
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.10,0:14:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗舰2 机动战士型10
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日晕联队 机动战士损失惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法维持战线
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让部署在前方的机动战士回去增援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最优先保护舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮如果继续对准歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.64,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被UE从背后攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果调头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后背又会暴露给歌姬号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第八宇宙舰队 正与UE交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是意想不到的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦军就交给UE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开这个宇域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往安巴德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 对同胞见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长不也说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避免消耗弹药和舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是千载难逢的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说 去营救敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再被抓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主炮准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动战士部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击眼前的UE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等这句话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付UE不用留情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号的机动战士部队…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走 这里有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当是安巴德的前哨站
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪我热个身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.79,0:16:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去安巴德教训UE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是怎么做到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像能看见敌人的轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发呆 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,技术不错啊 歌姬号的机师们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌姬号快速接近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,热能传感器确认主炮正在充能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜同归于尽 想击沉我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大战速离开歌姬号主炮的轴线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他们让路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你的 拿我的船当掩护打敌人措手不及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联络日晕 看守者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.33,0:18:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是舰队司令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全舰紧急调头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认射击系统同步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标更改为UE舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量充填准备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齐射 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许给我停！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:18:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 那么步调一致
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.76,0:19:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人战舰及机动战士型正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要命 总算赶跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你们救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弃我们而去的话明明可以轻松逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.25,0:19:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是在抗击UE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.63,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再有机会见面的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.15,0:19:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想与你喝一杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叛逃者古鲁迪克·艾诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们与UE交战间隙 趁乱逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是今天 在这里发生的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舰长 这…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样 不必多说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们好运 勇敢的叛逃者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗中发生过这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 我看见了敌人的行动轨迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像遇见柚铃的那次一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是X-Rounder的作用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Rounder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说联邦军正在研究
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类大脑中 一块掌管特殊能力的区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即所谓 X领域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人类一生也不会使用到的特殊区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果充分利用那块区域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以感知到常人无法感知的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.98,0:21:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有那种超感官的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.39,0:21:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫做X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.49,0:21:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你现在的能力确实异乎寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来就是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女孩真的是能力者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错 我能感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该知道我们此行的目的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括如果拒绝我们 你会有什么下场…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利特…
